{"tid":447573,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無同一種食物但烹調方法唔同,會食或唔食?","createTime":"2017-10-25T12:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T04:08:41.000Z","uid":115042,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6fb535968b5428a8b9f3441ea9327e6ed56804","tid":447573,"uid":115042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:00:14.000Z","msg":"自己例子:<br />\n冬菇,炆唔食,冬菇蠔豉個D<br />\n但燒冬菇就好鍾意食<br />\n<br />\n红蘿蔔,煲湯紅蘿蔔淋淋地口感好怪唔食<br />\n但細細條生紅蘿蔔爽爽甜甜好鍾意食<br />\n<br />\n洋葱,炸洋葱圈食,其他煮法唔食<br />\n<br />\n我咁算唔算偏食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c018b0371ada6d12e540f8ae4934614a18701c2","tid":447573,"uid":61417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:02:25.000Z","msg":"魚"},{"pid":"deca62ebe9a50d8b5cf8d126176104182eb5c363","tid":447573,"uid":105746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:02:35.000Z","msg":"我仲誇張過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到個蘿蔔切得大舊就唔想食<br />\n細細嚿我又接受到"},{"pid":"ac2751cb4eeb4faef674d2ba437fe5180df1c731","tid":447573,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:05:38.000Z","msg":"唔食一舊既蕃茄 但係食蕃茄醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45dfee5e45e0e03c052ed42dc8dbb0be2eac3c89","tid":447573,"uid":98483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:09:54.000Z","msg":"菠蘿生食先食到<br />\n煮熱咗之後個味怪怪地"},{"pid":"743e3ee7c9ff7610608a543d1032bd8b3418201c","tid":447573,"uid":5846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:20:55.000Z","msg":"紅蘿蔔湯渣我會食但係如果煲得唔夠淋我就好驚食"},{"pid":"6c5728d6a82b5c6551428b82162cab3726e1fe3a","tid":447573,"uid":18642,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:21:33.000Z","msg":"青瓜 煮熟左會唔鐘意食"},{"pid":"d95b97c6dcc3cee159cd19e4cdca99bbe347a18f","tid":447573,"uid":151684,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:01:47.000Z