ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T21:13:10.000Z","msg":"飲豆漿 食豆腐花 就係唔食豆腐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbce0b8289435f8a5c75a0304eae378b15812c4c","tid":447573,"uid":60539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T21:27:03.000Z","msg":"所有餸<br />\n老母煮會唔食<br />\n老豆煮會清晒<br />\n好神奇<br />\n明明係同樣既材料<br />\n只係落料既timing<br />\n火候既掌握<br />\n同埋一啲小技巧<br />\n可以完全係唔同層次"},{"pid":"dbc09fb1e88c6003caca44eec462f77e303d6a3f","tid":447573,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T22:12:29.000Z","msg":"青瓜 蕃茄 三文魚 煮熟既唔食<br />\n其他可以生食既都盡量生食"},{"pid":"10ec1b3e7ab1bc83ce005a1229fa1cb402d88949","tid":447573,"uid":108078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T22:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生木瓜<br />\n煲湯會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc2922c5f01292852e64c61ac3a740dc8807286","tid":447573,"uid":73366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己例子:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">冬菇,炆唔食,冬菇蠔豉個D<br />\n但燒冬菇就好鍾意食</span><br />\n<br />\n红蘿蔔,煲湯紅蘿蔔淋淋地口感好怪唔食<br />\n但細細條生紅蘿蔔爽爽甜甜好鍾意食<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">洋葱,炸洋葱圈食,其他煮法唔食</span><br />\n<br />\n我咁算唔算偏食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有蛋又係，蒸蛋炒蛋茶葉蛋都食，但煎蛋普通烚蛋就唔食蛋黃"},{"pid":"788831cf814a65aa3e3aca29acd0791dcb835a6c","tid":447573,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"屌我洋蔥同你一樣淨係食炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d630461269c95e06c49dce04e310861a91a0210","tid":447573,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:0